      "releaseNotes": "* App Intents | Now you can search, shop, and check your purchase history hands-free—just ask Siri or use iOS search with App Intents!\n* Fresh Picks Feature | Catch up on the latest items dropped in the last 30 days now on For You.\n* Sweat-free! | We’re always working hard to build a seamless app for you with continued bug fixes and performance improvements.",
